Try now!

1024
01:06:51.000 --> 01:06:51.833
[starter whirs]

1025
01:06:51.916 --> 01:06:54.125
[engine rumbling]

1026
01:06:54.208 --> 01:06:55.750
[laughing]

1027
01:06:55.833 --> 01:06:57.291
That's it! We got it!

1028
01:06:59.000 --> 01:07:00.958
