1033
01:07:16.458 --> 01:07:17.666
[yells]

1034
01:07:17.750 --> 01:07:19.083
Pull! Pull! Pull!

1035
01:07:19.166 --> 01:07:20.458
Come on!

1036
01:07:22.958 --> 01:07:24.208
