1039
01:07:33.541 --> 01:07:36.142
- [81] Nice work. Superman.
- [109] Let's get the hell out of here.

1040
01:07:36.166 --> 01:07:37.625
[60] Second that. brother.

1041
01:07:37.708 --> 01:07:39.583
Making the rest of us look bad.

1042
01:07:41.208 --> 01:07:44.083
Holy shit. Eighty-one made a joke.

1043
01:07:44.666 --> 01:07:47.375
Hey. dude bros.
Found Cadre's secret stash!

1044
01:07:47.458 --> 01:07:48.708
[60 whoops]

1045
01:07:48.791 --> 01:07:49.791
[109] Finally! Food.

1046
01:07:50.291 --> 01:07:51.976
- [81] You still with us?
- [60] Forty-four.

1047
01:07:52.000 --> 01:07:53.791
I ain't know I had a choice in that.

1048
01:07:54.666 --> 01:07:56.000
Let's get you home.

1049
01:07:56.083 --> 01:07:56.916
[15 grunts]

1050
01:07:57.000 --> 01:07:58.583
[flares firing]

1051
01:07:59.625 --> 01:08:02.083
[ominous music playing]

1052
01:08:02.166 --> 01:08:03.375
Oh shit.

1053
01:08:03.458 --> 01:08:05.791
- The Machine hit a tripwire!
- Check the perimeter!

1054
01:08:05.875 --> 01:08:08.000
- Get that winch in!
- [44] Sixty. move!

1055
01:08:08.916 --> 01:08:10.625
Get on that 50-cal. tanker!

1056
01:08:10.708 --> 01:08:12.041
Yeah. I'm on it!

1057
01:08:13.000 --> 01:08:14.000
[whirring]

1058
01:08:14.583 --> 01:08:15.708
[44] No. no. no. no. no!

1059
01:08:16.333 --> 01:08:17.875
- Come on.
- [engine rumbles]

1060
01:08:19.250 --> 01:08:20.791
I'm pulling in the winch!

1061
01:08:20.875 --> 01:08:22.000
[winch whirring]

1062
01:08:23.708 --> 01:08:25.041
[15 grunting]

1063
01:08:29.041 --> 01:08:30.791
Move! Move! Move! Move!

1064
01:08:30.875 --> 01:08:32.333
[flares firing]

1065
01:08:32.416 --> 01:08:35.166
[109] It's hit a second trip! Holy shit!

1066
01:08:35.250 --> 01:08:36.750
We gotta go!

1067
01:08:36.833 --> 01:08:38.041
We gotta move!

1068
01:08:38.125 --> 01:08:40.583
Fuck! There's no ammo in this bitch.

1069
01:08:40.666 --> 01:08:43.250
- I saw some back there.
- We don't have time. Fifteen!

1070
01:08:45.458 --> 01:08:48.916
- Where the hell is he going?
- Trying to be a goddamn hero.

1071
01:08:52.208 --> 01:08:53.500
[gasping]

1072
01:08:54.416 --> 01:08:56.416
[tense music playing]

1073
01:08:56.916 --> 01:08:58.458
[footsteps thudding]

1074
01:09:04.000 --> 01:09:05.250
Shit.

1075
01:09:05.833 --> 01:09:07.375
Fifteen. get your ass moving!

1076
01:09:14.791 --> 01:09:16.541
Fifteen. run!

1077
01:09:18.708 --> 01:09:20.833
[high-pitched ringing]

1078
01:09:22.833 --> 01:09:24.833
[109] Drive! Drive!

1079
01:09:24.916 --> 01:09:25.916
[60] Oh shit!

1080
01:09:25.958 --> 01:09:27.958
[intense music playing]

1081
01:09:29.083 --> 01:09:30.375
- [44 yells]
- [engine revving]

1082
01:09:33.958 --> 01:09:35.358
- [60] Give me the ammo!
- [109] Go!

1083
01:09:39.458 --> 01:09:40.791
Let's go. you piece of shit!

1084
01:09:47.750 --> 01:09:50.458
- It's catching up!
- They're all bouncing right off it.

1085
01:09:55.500 --> 01:09:56.791
[groans]

1086
01:09:56.875 --> 01:09:58.166
We need more speed!

1087
01:09:59.125 --> 01:10:00.375
[44] I'm redlining!

1088
01:10:00.458 --> 01:10:01.791
Hold on! [Yells]

1089
01:10:04.708 --> 01:10:06.666
[60] Come on. come on. come on!

1090
01:10:07.666 --> 01:10:08.875
[engine revs]

1091
01:10:10.500 --> 01:10:12.166
[60] Some armor plating on this bitch!

1092
01:10:14.583 --> 01:10:15.833
[gasps] Shit!

1093
01:10:15.916 --> 01:10:16.916
[81] Put that out!

1094
01:10:20.291 --> 01:10:22.166
[60] Our armor can't take any more!

1095
01:10:22.250 --> 01:10:23.958
I think we're losing it!

1096
01:10:27.583 --> 01:10:29.500
[60] Looks like it's falling back!

1097
01:10:29.583 --> 01:10:31.583
[suspenseful music playing]

1098
01:10:37.583 --> 01:10:38.750
Incoming!

1099
01:10:44.041 --> 01:10:45.583
[yells]

1100
01:10:47.000 --> 01:10:48.125
- [groans]
- [yelling]

1101
01:10:48.208 --> 01:10:49.291
Hold on! Hold on!

1102
01:10:49.375 --> 01:10:51.000
[intense music playing]

1103
01:10:55.750 --> 01:10:58.291
- Hold it fucking steady!
- I'm trying!

1104
01:11:20.666 --> 01:11:21.666
[grunting]

1105
01:11:24.791 --> 01:11:26.416
Hold on!

1106
01:11:30.208 --> 01:11:31.375
[grunting and yelling]

1107
01:11:31.458 --> 01:11:32.500
Fuck.

1108
01:11:33.666 --> 01:11:35.000
[grunting]

1109
01:11:39.958 --> 01:11:40.958
[44 yells]

1110
01:11:46.916 --> 01:11:49.041
[gasping]

1111
01:11:49.125 --> 01:11:52.041
[music crescendos. then fades]

1112
01:11:52.125 --> 01:11:54.833
Tell me we lost it. guys.
This transmission's smoked.

1113
01:11:54.916 --> 01:11:56.250
Sixty. you got eyes?

1114
01:11:56.916 --> 01:11:57.916
I can't see it.

1115
01:12:00.041 --> 01:12:01.708
I think we outran it.

1116
01:12:11.166 --> 01:12:13.166
[ominous music playing]

1117
01:12:19.708 --> 01:12:21.750
- Shit!
- [alert blaring]

1118
01:12:27.833 --> 01:12:29.625
[all yelling]

1119
01:12:30.958 --> 01:12:32.958
[intense music playing]

1120
01:12:36.500 --> 01:12:37.916
- It's pissed!
- Fight back!

1121
01:12:38.000 --> 01:12:39.375
[60] Yo. I'm trying!

1122
01:12:39.875 --> 01:12:41.125
Oh God.

1123
01:12:41.208 --> 01:12:44.666
- It's gotta have a weakness. right?
- [44] We're pissing hydraulic fluid!

1124
01:12:44.750 --> 01:12:46.500
Faster! Faster! Come on!

1125
01:12:46.583 --> 01:12:47.958
Hit it between the plates!

1126
01:12:53.750 --> 01:12:55.750
[intense music continues]

1127
01:13:06.125 --> 01:13:08.166
Hold her steady!

1128
01:13:08.250 --> 01:13:09.583
I'm working on it!

1129
01:13:13.541 --> 01:13:15.541
[screaming]

1130
01:13:18.666 --> 01:13:21.250
Oh God! [Wailing]

1131
01:13:45.208 --> 01:13:47.041
This thing is falling apart!

1132
01:14:00.916 --> 01:14:03.166
[81 grunting]

1133
01:14:04.833 --> 01:14:05.958
No!

1134
01:14:15.583 --> 01:14:16.583
Stop!

1135
01:14:17.333 --> 01:14:18.833
Hey. stop!

1136
01:14:29.291 --> 01:14:31.291
[music fades]

1137
01:14:33.166 --> 01:14:35.166
[dramatic. poignant music playing]

1138
01:14:58.583 --> 01:15:00.166
[heart beat thudding]

1139
01:15:00.250 --> 01:15:02.875
[younger brother] <i>Don't fucking quit.</i>

1140
01:15:03.375 --> 01:15:05.375
[gasping]

1141
01:15:05.458 --> 01:15:07.958
[thunder rumbling]

1142
01:15:11.000 --> 01:15:13.000
[haunting music playing]

1143
01:16:06.916 --> 01:16:08.916
[thunder rumbles]

1144
01:16:14.750 --> 01:16:16.500
[grunting]

1145
01:16:25.625 --> 01:16:26.625
What?

1146
01:16:27.750 --> 01:16:29.125
Where's the rest of it?

1147
01:16:34.500 --> 01:16:36.000
[warbling]

1148
01:16:41.458 --> 01:16:42.333
[grunts]

1149
01:16:42.416 --> 01:16:44.416
[music turns ominous]

1150
01:17:01.208 --> 01:17:03.125
Who the hell are you talking to?

1151
01:17:27.125 --> 01:17:28.166
Hey.

1152
01:17:28.250 --> 01:17:29.375
Hey. 7.

1153
01:17:30.000 --> 01:17:31.666
Hey. you with me?

1154
01:17:31.750 --> 01:17:32.916
[ammunition exploding]

1155
01:17:44.416 --> 01:17:46.416
[ominous music continues]

1156
01:17:52.000 --> 01:17:56.583
[sensor whirring]

1157
01:18:07.166 --> 01:18:09.458
[music crescendos. then fades]

1158
01:18:09.541 --> 01:18:11.541
[thunder rumbles]

1159
01:18:12.708 --> 01:18:14.708
[81 grunting]

1160
01:18:20.625 --> 01:18:22.625
[dramatic music playing]

1161
01:18:31.000 --> 01:18:33.000
[grunting]

1162
01:18:49.875 --> 01:18:50.875
[yells]

1163
01:18:52.250 --> 01:18:53.583
[yells]

1164
01:18:59.166 --> 01:19:00.291
Fuck!

1165
01:19:03.166 --> 01:19:04.208
Fuck!

1166
01:19:05.500 --> 01:19:07.250
Fuck!

1167
01:19:13.333 --> 01:19:14.666
[yelling]

1168
01:19:16.708 --> 01:19:17.791
[grunts]

1169
01:19:18.708 --> 01:19:20.416
[yelling]

1170
01:19:21.958 --> 01:19:22.958
[groans]

1171
01:19:23.500 --> 01:19:26.250
Fuck! Fuck! You fucked me!

1172
01:19:26.333 --> 01:19:28.541
- Fuck!
- [watch beeping]

1173
01:19:32.666 --> 01:19:35.166
You suck. you fucking piece of shit.

1174
01:19:58.208 --> 01:20:00.666
[sobs softly]

1175
01:20:01.750 --> 01:20:03.291
I knew who you were…

1176
01:20:05.500 --> 01:20:07.625
The moment I saw you on that bus.

1177
01:20:08.375 --> 01:20:11.625
I went through Air Assault
with a loudmouth private.

1178
01:20:11.708 --> 01:20:13.708
[poignant music playing]

1179
01:20:14.291 --> 01:20:16.625
Got this dumb tattoo on his arm.

1180
01:20:19.791 --> 01:20:21.250
"D.F.Q."

1181
01:20:27.458 --> 01:20:29.041
You knew my brother?

1182
01:20:31.666 --> 01:20:34.416
He wouldn't shut up
about becoming a Ranger with you.

1183
01:20:37.916 --> 01:20:40.416
I was on furlough when I heard he passed.

1184
01:20:43.541 --> 01:20:45.000
Why didn't you tell me?

1185
01:20:47.000 --> 01:20:48.083
I tried.

1186
01:20:55.125 --> 01:20:56.583
I just thought. uh…

1187
01:21:02.208 --> 01:21:04.916
If I could get across
that finish line for him…

1188
01:21:08.041 --> 01:21:09.875
Maybe it could help me sleep.

1189
01:21:13.458 --> 01:21:15.208
You think you failed your brother?

1190
01:21:17.875 --> 01:21:19.375
I failed everybody.

1191
01:21:20.958 --> 01:21:22.708
But you never gave up.

1192
01:21:24.416 --> 01:21:26.000
That's not failure.

1193
01:21:28.458 --> 01:21:29.833
That's a Ranger.

1194
01:21:39.291 --> 01:21:41.291
[sensor whirring]

1195
01:21:43.583 --> 01:21:45.375
[music turns ominous]

1196
01:21:51.833 --> 01:21:53.666
[81] That thing doesn't quit either.

1197
01:21:53.750 --> 01:21:56.041
How the fuck
are we supposed to stop this thing?

1198
01:21:56.125 --> 01:21:57.750
What would your brother do?

1199
01:21:57.833 --> 01:21:59.791
[thunder rumbles]

1200
01:22:01.583 --> 01:22:03.583
Probably fill it with Stop Leak.

1201
01:22:04.083 --> 01:22:06.083
[both laughing]

1202
01:22:21.583 --> 01:22:22.583
Wait.

1203
01:22:23.208 --> 01:22:26.166
- It's venting.
- What does that mean?

1204
01:22:26.250 --> 01:22:28.250
[music turns dramatic]

1205
01:22:31.833 --> 01:22:33.083
I got an idea.

1206
01:22:33.666 --> 01:22:35.916
[both grunting]

1207
01:22:36.000 --> 01:22:38.875
- Can you wait here for me?
- Yeah. I can wait.

1208
01:22:39.375 --> 01:22:41.375
[thunder crashes]

1209
01:22:43.458 --> 01:22:45.458
[81 grunting]

1210
01:23:06.708 --> 01:23:08.708
[dramatic music playing]

1211
01:23:41.166 --> 01:23:42.291
[beeping]

1212
01:23:52.166 --> 01:23:53.416
Where are the rocks?

1213
01:23:53.500 --> 01:23:55.375
Cone crusher.

1214
01:23:55.458 --> 01:23:57.791
This is… How the fuck do you turn this on?

1215
01:24:14.333 --> 01:24:16.375
Thermodynamics. motherfucker.

1216
01:24:17.333 --> 01:24:19.333
[footsteps thudding]

1217
01:24:40.041 --> 01:24:41.750
[tense music playing]

1218
01:25:11.583 --> 01:25:12.791
[music fades]

1219
01:25:19.916 --> 01:25:21.916
[thunder rumbling]

1220
01:25:22.958 --> 01:25:24.958
[dark music playing]

1221
01:26:01.875 --> 01:26:03.875
[explosives beeping]

1222
01:26:22.708 --> 01:26:24.166
Come on!

1223
01:26:29.375 --> 01:26:30.375
[grunts]

1224
01:26:31.541 --> 01:26:32.625
[grunts]

1225
01:26:35.083 --> 01:26:36.291
You want a piece of me?

1226
01:26:36.375 --> 01:26:38.375
[intense music playing]

1227
01:27:09.125 --> 01:27:10.750
No! [Grunts]

1228
01:27:15.083 --> 01:27:16.000
[yells]

1229
01:27:16.083 --> 01:27:17.958
No. No!

1230
01:27:19.833 --> 01:27:20.833
Come on!

1231
01:27:21.958 --> 01:27:22.958
No. no. no.

1232
01:27:24.166 --> 01:27:25.458
[yells]

1233
01:27:31.708 --> 01:27:32.958
[yells]

1234
01:27:33.916 --> 01:27:35.916
[intense music continues]

1235
01:27:43.125 --> 01:27:44.125
Breathe. you fucker!

1236
01:27:46.583 --> 01:27:48.000
Stop Leak. bitch.

1237
01:28:04.916 --> 01:28:06.291
[alarms blaring]

1238
01:28:06.375 --> 01:28:07.375
Oh…

1239
01:28:10.666 --> 01:28:11.666
[yells]

1240
01:28:17.958 --> 01:28:19.333
Yes!

1241
01:28:24.958 --> 01:28:26.166
Stay with me!

1242
01:28:42.958 --> 01:28:44.166
[yells]

1243
01:28:44.250 --> 01:28:45.666
[grunts]

1244
01:28:45.750 --> 01:28:47.750
[intense music continues]

1245
01:29:01.708 --> 01:29:02.708
[gasps]

1246
01:29:16.791 --> 01:29:18.791
[music fades]

1247
01:29:24.750 --> 01:29:25.916
[exhales]

1248
01:29:31.916 --> 01:29:33.833
[ominous music playing]

1249
01:29:37.750 --> 01:29:39.291
You gotta be shitting me.

1250
01:29:40.708 --> 01:29:42.708
[music turns tense]

1251
01:29:45.583 --> 01:29:47.250
[whirring]

1252
01:30:01.875 --> 01:30:03.875
[music fades]

1253
01:30:08.500 --> 01:30:10.500
[dramatic music playing]

1254
01:30:22.416 --> 01:30:24.416
[breathing heavily]

1255
01:30:30.125 --> 01:30:32.500
[helicopters whirring]

1256
01:30:44.291 --> 01:30:46.291
[dramatic music continues]

1257
01:30:54.375 --> 01:30:55.875
[indistinct radio chatter]

1258
01:30:55.958 --> 01:30:57.750
[speaks indistinctly]

1259
01:31:01.958 --> 01:31:03.958
[dramatic music intensifies]

1260
01:31:39.583 --> 01:31:40.833
[grunting]

1261
01:31:40.916 --> 01:31:42.166
[groaning]

1262
01:31:51.000 --> 01:31:52.125
All the way.

1263
01:31:54.375 --> 01:31:55.791
All the way. brother.

1264
01:31:57.708 --> 01:31:59.588
[soldier 1] Hey. there's more
injured over here!

1265
01:31:59.666 --> 01:32:00.916
[soldier 2] Let's go!

1266
01:32:04.041 --> 01:32:05.958
Lift him up! Let's go!

1267
01:32:08.458 --> 01:32:10.458
[dramatic music continues]

1268
01:32:27.750 --> 01:32:29.000
[Sergeant Major] Candidate.

1269
01:32:31.125 --> 01:32:32.666
Are you all that's left?

1270
01:32:35.041 --> 01:32:36.750
[somber music playing]

1271
01:32:38.791 --> 01:32:41.458
I'm sorry we couldn't reach you sooner.

1272
01:32:42.458 --> 01:32:46.458
We only just secured this base.
We lost half the battalion.

1273
01:32:49.291 --> 01:32:50.500
How many are there?

1274
01:32:51.250 --> 01:32:52.375
They're everywhere.

1275
01:32:52.458 --> 01:32:55.041
We've neutralized the first wave.

1276
01:32:55.750 --> 01:32:58.916
But we're preparing for a global invasion.

1277
01:33:00.583 --> 01:33:04.166
{\an8}[man on TV] <i>36 hours ago.</i>
<i>what NASA believed to be an asteroid</i>

1278
01:33:04.250 --> 01:33:08.750
{\an8}<i>split into countless pods
that impacted sites across the globe.</i>

1279
01:33:08.833 --> 01:33:12.458
{\an8}<i>These pods transformed
into deadly machines…</i>

1280
01:33:12.541 --> 01:33:13.833
Pupils reactive and equal.

1281
01:33:13.916 --> 01:33:16.458
<i>…attacking cities. civilians.
and defense networks alike.</i>

1282
01:33:16.541 --> 01:33:20.125
<i>But just as the world's militaries
managed to contain the threat.</i>

1283
01:33:20.208 --> 01:33:22.666
<i>interstellar imaging
confirms our worst fear.</i>

1284
01:33:22.750 --> 01:33:23.583
[medic] Your fingers.

1285
01:33:23.666 --> 01:33:26.500
<i>Tens of thousands more are on their way.</i>

1286
01:33:26.583 --> 01:33:29.833
{\an8}<i>A coordinated global response
is now being launched.</i>

1287
01:33:29.916 --> 01:33:34.250
{\an8}<i>with allied forces mobilizing
across air. land. and sea.</i>

1288
01:33:34.333 --> 01:33:38.375
<i>We don't know what they want.
We don't know why they're here.</i>

1289
01:33:38.458 --> 01:33:40.083
<i>But every nation on Earth…</i>

1290
01:33:40.166 --> 01:33:41.000
[soldier] Corporal.

1291
01:33:41.083 --> 01:33:42.416
<i>…Is now preparing for war.</i>

1292
01:33:42.500 --> 01:33:43.916
We're ready to see you now.

1293
01:33:45.375 --> 01:33:46.775
[Torres] <i>A global military alliance</i>

1294
01:33:46.833 --> 01:33:48.791
<i>is about to launch
our first counteroffensive.</i>

1295
01:33:48.875 --> 01:33:51.916
Only problem is we've thrown
everything we have at these things.

1296
01:33:52.000 --> 01:33:53.625
These machines don't die easy.

1297
01:33:53.708 --> 01:33:55.625
[Sergeant Major] What we need to know is.

1298
01:33:55.708 --> 01:33:59.250
how the hell did you take one down
without any weapons?

1299
01:34:01.041 --> 01:34:03.041
Like you said. Sergeant Major.

1300
01:34:04.083 --> 01:34:06.125
Every machine has its limits.

1301
01:34:07.833 --> 01:34:09.708
The primary venting port here.

1302
01:34:10.708 --> 01:34:12.416
Like a radiator in a Humvee.

1303
01:34:13.208 --> 01:34:15.500
If you jam it hard enough.
the whole system chokes.

1304
01:34:15.583 --> 01:34:17.916
[pensive music playing]

1305
01:34:18.000 --> 01:34:19.958
Get CENTCOM on the line.

1306
01:34:20.041 --> 01:34:22.291
Torres. you heard the man.
Let's saddle up!

1307
01:34:22.375 --> 01:34:23.416
[Torres] I'm on it.

1308
01:34:25.791 --> 01:34:28.291
Your intel's gonna save a lot of lives.

1309
01:34:29.833 --> 01:34:31.833
You were right. Sergeant Major.

1310
01:34:33.583 --> 01:34:34.708
I wasn't ready.

1311
01:34:35.375 --> 01:34:37.708
[dramatic. poignant music playing]

1312
01:34:42.916 --> 01:34:44.083
You are now.

1313
01:34:47.208 --> 01:34:48.833
Welcome to the Regiment.

1314
01:34:53.208 --> 01:34:55.125
Your brother'd be proud.

1315
01:34:57.916 --> 01:35:00.541
[Torres] Rangers. kit up!
We're moving out! Let's go!

1316
01:35:03.541 --> 01:35:07.041
You know. they're all talking
about what you did out there.

1317
01:35:07.875 --> 01:35:13.000
If you got it in you. son.
I'm sure they'd appreciate a few words.

1318
01:35:15.458 --> 01:35:17.083
[Torres] Rangers have been tasked

1319
01:35:17.166 --> 01:35:19.458
as the spearhead
of Operation Global Shield.

1320
01:35:19.541 --> 01:35:24.458
Joining a full-scale military mobilization
across air. land. and sea.

1321
01:35:24.541 --> 01:35:29.166
Your Black Hawks escorted by F-35 fighters
will drop you on the city outskirts.

1322
01:35:29.791 --> 01:35:34.666
Your mission is to clear civilians
and make way for heavy ordnance.

1323
01:35:35.500 --> 01:35:38.500
United States military's
never faced an enemy like this.

1324
01:35:39.416 --> 01:35:41.083
But we're gonna rise to the occasion.

1325
01:35:41.166 --> 01:35:43.625
[determined music playing]

1326
01:35:57.125 --> 01:35:59.541
I know how some of you are feeling.

1327
01:36:01.083 --> 01:36:02.083
Hurt.

1328
01:36:03.833 --> 01:36:04.875
Tired.

1329
01:36:06.666 --> 01:36:08.083
Maybe even scared.

1330
01:36:09.875 --> 01:36:12.500
But we are Rangers.

1331
01:36:13.666 --> 01:36:14.791
We fight for each other.

1332
01:36:16.708 --> 01:36:19.416
And we fight for those
who never made it home.

1333
01:36:20.750 --> 01:36:22.208
We don't back down.

1334
01:36:23.791 --> 01:36:25.208
We don't break.

1335
01:36:26.416 --> 01:36:29.583
And we sure as hell don't fucking quit.

1336
01:36:29.666 --> 01:36:31.208
[in unison] Hell yeah!

1337
01:36:31.291 --> 01:36:32.958
Rangers lead the way!

1338
01:36:33.041 --> 01:36:34.750
[in unison] All the way!

1339
01:36:34.833 --> 01:36:36.416
[music intensifies]

1340
01:37:07.458 --> 01:37:12.083
[soldier] <i>All CA elements. check in.</i>
<i>This is Chalk Leader Fox 1. spinning up.</i>

1341
01:37:12.166 --> 01:37:13.541
[pilot 1] <i>Fox 2. up and ready.</i>

1342
01:37:13.625 --> 01:37:15.416
[pilot 2] <i>Fox 3. standing by.</i>

1343
01:37:16.958 --> 01:37:19.666
[dramatic music playing]

1344
01:37:28.708 --> 01:37:31.750
[officer on comm] <i>Black Hawk squadron.</i>
<i>you are green across the board.</i>

1345
01:37:31.833 --> 01:37:33.750
<i>F-35s have your escort.</i>

1346
01:37:33.833 --> 01:37:36.291
<i>Operation Global Shield is live.</i>

1347
01:37:36.375 --> 01:37:38.208
<i>Godspeed. Rangers.</i>

1348
01:37:39.791 --> 01:37:43.291
Chalk Leader Fox 1
with seven packs on board.

1349
01:37:43.375 --> 01:37:46.750
McQueen. Lieberman. Young. Janus. Cook.

1350
01:37:50.458 --> 01:37:53.208
Hey! Anybody catch his name?

1351
01:38:01.291 --> 01:38:04.291
[dramatic music continues]

1352
01:39:38.208 --> 01:39:39.208
[music fades]

1353
01:39:39.291 --> 01:39:41.291
[intense music playing]

1354
01:41:08.291 --> 01:41:10.291
[music turns ominous]

1355
01:42:03.916 --> 01:42:05.916
[music turns dramatic]

1356
01:43:06.791 --> 01:43:08.791
[music turns poignant]

1357
01:44:53.708 --> 01:44:55.708
[music turns dramatic]

1358
01:46:29.166 --> 01:46:31.166
[music fades]

1359
01:46:32.305 --> 01:47:32.339
